---
title: Carb Smart Beef-Stuffed Peppers with Couscous and Side Salad
description: A mix of spiced beef and couscous makes a wonderful filling for Middle Eastern-inspired stuffed peppers. This carb smart dinner is full of wholesome veggies.

Carb Smart (50 g carbohydrates or less) is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's carbohydrate amount.

Ingredients: Ground beef • Green pepper • Sweet bell pepper • Roma tomatoes • Moroccan couscous (durum wheat semolina) (wheat) • Feta cheese (pasteurized milk, partly skimmed milk, water, salt, lipase, bacterial culture, microbial enzyme, cellulose, natamycin, calcium chloride) (milk) • Spinach • Yogurt sauce (cream, pasteurized milk, milk protein concentrate, yogurt (partly skimmed milk, skim milk powder, bacterial culture), sour cream (milk ingredients, modified corn starch, guar gum, carrageenan, locust bean gum, sodium citrate, bacterial culture), cucumber, garlic, lemon, vinegar, modified cornstarch, water, canola oil, salt, white pepper, herbs, potassium sorbate) (milk) • Turkish spice blend (paprika powder, spices, onion powder, garlic powder, salt, herbs, oleoresin paprika, canola oil, silicon dioxide) (sulphites) • Red wine vinegar (wine vinegar, potassium sorbate, sulphites) (sulphites) • Parsley.
